Quality is great but I have to offer a word of advice to my Law Enforcement brothers and sisters. While this movie realistically shows the daily life and struggles of LEO's, the ending to this movie hits too close to home for most of us who have lost brothers in war or on the streets. DO NOT watch this movie with your family or around other people. Watch it once, enjoy it once for what it is and scrap it or better yet...as great of a movie as this is in so many ways, it might be better to just skip this one if you fit the previously stated profile.
